<section class="section contrast reveal" aria-labelledby="compare-title">
  <div class="section-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">Why this matters</p>
    <h2 id="compare-title">From AI coding helpers to full lifecycle operations</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="compare-grid">
    <article>
      <h3>Prompt-only execution</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Unstable behavior between runs and operators</li>
        <li>No mandatory evidence quality threshold</li>
        <li>Hard to review, replay, and recover incidents</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>agentic-sdlc control plane</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Deterministic, policy-driven workflow execution</li>
        <li>Structured report + quality gate before finalize</li>
        <li>Resumable, traceable, audit-friendly delivery loop</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

